title: Super Bowl Preview Extravaganza!!
itunes:title: Super Bowl Preview Extravaganza!!
description:
A room filled with heroes- Dan Hanzus, Marc Sessler, Gregg Rosenthal & Chris Wesseling- bring you the ultimate Super Bowl Preview Extravaganza straight from Room 519 of an undisclosed hotel. The heroes react to the Chiefs trading QB Alex Smith and what it means for the rest of the league (7:00); Dan makes a BREAKING NEWS announcement about his future (22:00); A comprehensive preview of the Super Bowl (28:00); And the annual GO GET MY LUNCH Super Bowl props (58:00).

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
